3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 
3 3 3 3 3 3 3 3 ) \ ? SETUP "SYS-OPTIONS" ? ? SETUP "ACCOUNT-INFO" ? ? SETUP 
"RUN-CONTROL" ? ? SETUP DESCRIPTION ? \ DESCRIP DESCRIP = ( 
"STAMICARBON CO2 STRIPPING PROCESS H.P. SYNTHESIS SECTION" " " 
"This model simulates the high-pressure synthesis loop of a plant to" 
"produce urea by the Stamicarbon CO2-stripping process." " " 
"The simulation is based upon a closed-loop flowsheet.  The" 
"downstream section is approximated by using a SEP block to link" 
"the Stripper bottom urea solution (S09) to the recycled carbamate soluti" 
"on (S13)." ) \ ? ODATABANKS ? \ ODATABANKS AUTO-PARAM = YES \ ? "DATA-SERVICE" 
? ? DATABANKS ? \ DATABANKS FILE-SYM-NAM = ( "APV140 AQUEOUS" "APV140 ASPENPCD" 
