";This Urea Synthesis Reactor uses a User model that " 
";has two real parameters as input.  These control " 
";the relative rates of the two reactions that " ";occur:" 
";1.  2NH3 + CO2 <-->  CARB" ";2.  CARB <-->  UREA + H2O" 
";The two real parameters are as follows:" 
";Par #  Description                Default Value" 
";1      Relative rate of Rxn 1     1.0" 
";2      Relative rate of Rxn 2     1.0" 
";The procedure for adjusting the two input " 
";parameters is to make Par #1 large enough to keep " 
";Rxn #1 at equilibrium, and then to adjust Par #1 " 
";to describe the conversion in the reactor." ) \ ? BLOCK PUMP B13 ? ; 
